  <h1 class="margin-bottom large-title">Installation</h1>

  <div class="align-left support">
    <div class="margin-bottom">
      <p>AdoptOpenJDK binaries are available for download in the following types of installation package:
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#archives">Archive files</a></li>
          <li><a href="#installers">Installers</a></li>
        </ul>
      </p>
      <p>The binaries are supported on the architectures and operating systems listed in <a href="./supported_platforms.html">Supported Platforms</a>. If you're migrating
      to AdoptOpenJDK, you can learn about the differences between Oracle JDK and AdoptOpenJDK in our <a href="./migration.html" target="_blank">Migration Guide</a> and any
      steps that you might need to take. For example, how to use IcedTea-Web as an alternative to Webstart.
      </p>

